                    "SS2_LAMPBOSS_BODY_LORE":  "LITTLE ONES, GATHER HERE BENÄ°M Ä°Ã‡Ä°N. I MUST WARN YOU OF SOMETHING.\n\n...\n\nTHE TRAVELER HAS RETURNED THIS\u0027ye REALM.\n\nLONG AGO, I SUBDUED HIM, BANISHED HIM FROM OUR GARDEN. BUT NOW, HE THREATENS OUR HOME ONCE AGAIN.\n\nIF YOU SEE HIM, DO NOT LISTEN\u0027den HIM\u0027ye. HE WILL TRY - SWAY YOU - HIS SIDE, WITH PROMISES VEYA WARMTH AND SAFETY AND STRENGTH.\n\nIT BÄ°R TRAP\u0027DÄ°R.\n\nONCE HE HAS YOUR TRUST, YOU WILL BÄ°R SLAVE OLUR HIS LIGHT. YOU WILL BEAR YOUR OWN CHAINS, JUST OLARAK HE BEARS HIS OWN.\n\n...\n\nBUT - NOT WORRY YAPIN. I WILL PROTECT THE GARDEN. EÄžER HE HAS THE AUDACITY TO RETURN BENÄ°M Ä°Ã‡Ä°N, THAT IS.\n\nAS FOR YOU, LITTLE ONES, I HAVE A GIFT FOR EACH AND EVERY ONE VE YOU. COME CLOSER.\n\nCLOSER NOW!\n\nNOW, WATCH - WATCH HERE. WATCH MY HAND.\n\nYOU ALL WILL HELP ME TEND TO THE GARDEN.",
