                    "SS2_NEMCAPTAIN_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Captain issues orders to control the battlefield and fight safely from behind his Adaptive Microbots.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Keep your cool. Using Orders too quickly will build Stress, leaving you vulnerable.\n\nThis mod was translated by: Jaosnake",
