                    "SS2_ITEM_MOLTENCOIN_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e6%\u003c/style\u003e ihtimalle dÃ¼ÅŸmanlarÄ± vurulduÄŸunda \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003etutuÅŸtur\u003c/style\u003e taban hasarÄ±n \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e200%\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(birikim baÅŸÄ±na +50%)\u003c/style\u003e kadar hasar ver ve \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e$1\u003c/style\u003e \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(birikim baÅŸÄ±na +$1, temizlenmiÅŸ aÅŸamalara gÃ¶re artar).",
