                    "SS2_ITEM_NANOBOTS_DESC":  "\u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003e{0} \u003cstyle=cStack\u003e(+{0} birikim baÅŸÄ±na)\u003c/style\u003e zÄ±rh\u003c/style\u003e kazan. Hurdaya ayrÄ±lÄ±nca, hurdacÄ±yÄ± bu eÅŸyanÄ±n bir kopyasÄ±na \u003cstyle=cIsUtility\u003edÃ¶nÃ¼ÅŸtÃ¼r\u003c/style\u003e.",
