                    "SS2_KNIGHT_UTILITY_LEAP_DESC":  "Ä°sabet baÅŸÄ±na \u003cstyle=cIsDamage\u003e%120 hasar\u003c/style\u003e iÃ§in tekrar tekrar ileri atÄ±lÄ±r, dÃ¶ner ve dilimler. VuruÅŸ sayÄ±sÄ± saldÄ±rÄ± hÄ±zÄ±na gÃ¶re artar.",
