                    "SS2_KEYWORD_EXECUTING2":  "\u003cstyle=cKeywordName\u003eEyÃ¼rÃ¼tme\u003c/style\u003e\u003cstyle=cSub\u003eBirden fazla dÃ¼ÅŸman vurulmazsa hasar ve tetiklenme katsayÄ±sÄ± iki katÄ±na Ã§Ä±kar. Ä°ki kat kazanÄ±lan Ä°yon ManipÃ¼latÃ¶rÃ¼ stoklarÄ±nÄ± Ã¶ldÃ¼rÃ¼r.\u003c/style\u003e",
