                    "SS2_EVENT_BLAZINGELITE_END":  "KÄ±zgÄ±n sÄ±caklÄ±k daÄŸÄ±lÄ±yor...",
                    "SS2_NEMMANDO_DESCRIPTION":  "The Nemesis Commando is a wildcard on the battlefield, capable of turning any situation to his favor.\n\n\u003ccolor=#CCD3E0\u003e\u003c ! \u003e Blade of Cessation is risky but can build up a lot of damage by stacking Gouge.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Distant Gash can be used to safely apply stacks of Gouge to groups of enemies - take advantage of its piercing!\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Proper balance of melee and ranged combat is key, and Tactical Roll grants high armor to help enter and exit battles.\n\n\u003c ! \u003e Submission can be utilized as huge burst of damage, whether it be to aid in an escape or get the jump on an unsuspecting target.\n\nThis mod was translated by: Jaosnake",
